ina (located mainly in present-day Sichuan province)."]}]},{"name":"Touche","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  French Anastasie, Denys, Evest, Minos, Rodolph, Vernice.","French: topographic name for someone who lived by a small grove, from a diminutive of Old French <i>toche</i> ‘grove’.","History: René Touchet from Thorigné-d'Anjou in Maine-et-Loire, France, married Marie Caillé in Saint-Laurent, Île-de-Montreal, QC, in 1746."],"variants":[{"name":"Touchette","meanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  French Lucien, Marcel, Pierre, Armand, Collette, Euclide, Henri, Hilaire, Huguette.","Altered form of French   Touchet  , reflecting the Canadian and American French practice of sounding the final <i>-t</i>."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"La Touche was born in 1205. She had at least 2 sons with John Wakeman."},"et":{"1205–":"1205–Surnud","1380–1460":"1380–1460","1400–Male":"1400–Surnud","1403–1437":"1403–1437","1205–Female":"1205–Surnud","1437":"1437","1205":"1205","1403":"1403","1400":"1400","1460":"1460","1380":"1380","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","of Cheddington, Buckingham, England":"Cheddington, Buckinghamshire, England"},"fi":{"1205–":"1205–Kuollut","1380–1460":"1380–1460","1400–Male":"1400–Kuollut","1403–1437":"1403–1437","1205–Female":"1205–Kuollut","1437":"1437","1205":"1205","1403":"1403","1400":"1400","1460":"1460","1380":"1380","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","of Cheddington, Buckingham, England":"Cheddington, Buckinghamshire, England"},"fr":{"1205–":"1205–Décédée","1380–1460":"1380–1460","1400–Male":"1400–Décédé","1403–1437":"1403–1437","1205–Female":"1205–Décédée","1437":"1437","1205":"1205","1403":"1403","1400":"1400","1460":"1460","1380":"1380","Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","of Cheddington, Buckingham, England":"Cheddington, Buckingham